Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.39,0:27:31.28,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}たいせつを奏でよう
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.64,0:27:55.23,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}うれしくって泣いた　痛くって笑った
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.65,0:28:04.12,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}だけどそんな全部が生きてる証なんです
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.52,0:28:08.63,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ゆっくり歩いていこう
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.66,0:28:10.19,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Everybody singing!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.49,0:28:14.70,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ひとさじの本音　聞かせて？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.70,0:28:16.07,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}You're just my friend
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.09,0:28:22.02,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}愛情×友情　時に揺れても
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.04,0:28:22.02,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I know, You know little happy
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.02,0:28:27.88,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ずっとずっと　響きあいたい
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.96,0:28:27.88,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Can you hear my precious note?
